# For Curious Priest Quest - FW
if hascondition trigger shadowman
     chat trigger "You hear him mumbling something, you can only make out Find Dark Ones."
     chat trigger "What could he possibly mean?"
     endscrpit
end
chat trigger "As you step closer you begin to quiver in fear."
chat trigger "You know that you're stronger than him, but his brimstone eyes make you think twice about going near him."
addcondition trigger shadowman
inc trigger locx -2
endscript



